{"k":"macOS-High-Sierra-install-PHP-Apache-note","t":"2017 macOS High Sierra 安裝 PHP Apache 筆記","i":"2017-11-27","a":[{"e":"p","t":"最近因為需要開發 iOS App 所以逼得我自己需要把 Mac OS 更新到最新版本，但更新完後發現內建在 OSX 中的 PHP 版本居然變成了 7，變成 PHP 7 是不打緊，只是我需要的 PHP-imagick 套件一直安裝不起來，覺得氣餒，所以為了解決這問題下了一點點功課。"},{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"基本上在網路上找相關的解法都是用 "},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://brew.sh/index_zh-tw.html","target":"_blank"},"t":"Homebrew"},{"e":"span","t":" 來解決這項問題，找了大半天終於讓我找到一篇完整的介紹，以下就用"},{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://getgrav.org/blog/macos-sierra-apache-multiple-php-versions","target":"_blank"},"t":"此篇"},{"e":"span","t":"來說明利用 Homebrew 來針對 PHP 版本控制的方法吧！"}]},{"e":"h3","t":"環境設定"},{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"更新 xcode command line，終端機下 "},{"e":"code","t":"xcode-select --install"}]},{"e":"h3","t":"安裝 Homebrew"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"安裝 Homebrew "},{"e":"code","t":"ruby -e \"$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)\""}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"顯示版本 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew --version"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"檢查 "},{"e":"code","t":"Brew brew doctor"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"執行設定 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew tap homebrew/php"},{"e":"span","t":"，Tap 的用意是之後就不用再打 "},{"e":"code","t":"homebrew/php"},{"e":"span","t":"，例如 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install homebrew/php/php71 --with-apache"},{"e":"span","t":"，就可以直接 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install php71 --with-apache"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"更新 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew brew update"}]}]},{"e":"h3","t":"移除停止使用 mac 原生的 Apache"},{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"先暫停 Apache "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl stop"},{"e":"span","t":" 與 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo launchctl unload -w /System/Library/LaunchDaemons/org.apache.httpd.plist 2&gt;/dev/null"}]},{"e":"h3","t":"安裝新的 Apache"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"用 Brew 安裝 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install httpd"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"啟動 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo brew services start httpd"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"設定 "},{"e":"code","t":"ps -aef | grep httpd"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"重開 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl -k restart"}]}]},{"e":"h3","t":"新 Apache 指令"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"開啟 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl start"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"關閉 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl stop"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"重開 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl -k restart"}]}]},{"e":"h3","t":"新 Apache 相關設定"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"編輯 "},{"e":"code","t":"/usr/local/etc/httpd/httpd.conf"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"修改一下項目"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","t":"Listen 80"},{"e":"li","t":"DocumentRoot \"/usr/local/var/www\""},{"e":"li","t":"LoadModule rewrite_module lib/httpd/modules/mod_rewrite.so"},{"e":"li","t":"ServerName localhost"}]}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"重開 Apache "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl -k restart"}]}]},{"e":"h3","t":"安裝各版本的 PHP"},{"e":"p","t":"重新安裝記得 unlink 然後是下 reinstall 安裝 php，安裝會比較久別擔心。"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"安裝 5.6 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install php56 --with-httpd"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"先移除 5.6 設定 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew unlink php56"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"安裝 7.0 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install php70 --with-httpd"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"先移除 7.0 設定 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew unlink php70"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"安裝 7.1 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install php71 --with-httpd"}]}]},{"e":"p","t":"可以順便安裝相關套件如 mcrypt、imagick、redis，各版本指令如下："},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"5.6 版本 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install php56-mcrypt php56-imagick php56-redis"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"7.0 版本 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install php70-mcrypt php70-imagick php70-redis"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"7.1 版本 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew install php71-mcrypt php71-imagick php71-redis"}]}]},{"e":"p","t":"各版本的 php.ini 分別在："},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"5.6 版本 "},{"e":"code","t":"/usr/local/etc/php/5.6/php.ini"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"7.0 版本 "},{"e":"code","t":"/usr/local/etc/php/7.0/php.ini"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"7.1 版本 "},{"e":"code","t":"/usr/local/etc/php/7.1/php.ini"}]}]},{"e":"h3","t":"更改 CLI 的 php 版本，以下以更改 5.6 為例"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"因最後一個 install 的是 7.1 所以記得移除 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew unlink php71"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"改使用 5.6 "},{"e":"code","t":"brew link php56"}]}]},{"e":"p","t":"※ 注意！這裡只有改到 cli 部分，Apache 還沒改掉所以 phpinfo 出來應該還是 7.1"},{"e":"h3","t":"更改 Apache 的 php 版本"},{"e":"p","t":"以下以更改 5.6 為例"},{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"打開編輯 "},{"e":"code","t":"/usr/local/etc/httpd/httpd.conf"},{"e":"span","t":" 會發現多出如下："}]},{"e":"pre","s":[{"e":"code","t":"LoadModule php5_module /usr/local/Cellar/php56/5.6.31_7/libexec/apache2/libphp5.so\nLoadModule php7_module /usr/local/Cellar/php70/7.0.24_16/libexec/apache2/libphp7.so\nLoadModule php7_module /usr/local/Cellar/php71/7.1.10_21/libexec/apache2/libphp7.so"}]},{"e":"p","t":"將其改成"},{"e":"pre","s":[{"e":"code","t":"LoadModule php5_module /usr/local/opt/php56/libexec/apache2/libphp5.so\nLoadModule php7_module /usr/local/opt/php70/libexec/apache2/libphp7.so\nLoadModule php7_module /usr/local/opt/php71/libexec/apache2/libphp7.so"}]},{"e":"p","t":"但只能一個，因為要以 5.6 為例子，所以其他註解起來"},{"e":"pre","s":[{"e":"code","t":"LoadModule php5_module /usr/local/opt/php56/libexec/apache2/libphp5.so\n#LoadModule php7_module /usr/local/opt/php70/libexec/apache2/libphp7.so\n#LoadModule php7_module /usr/local/opt/php71/libexec/apache2/libphp7.so"}]},{"e":"p","t":"※ 注意！這裡改的是 Apache 部分，CLI 則不是這樣改的～"},{"e":"p","t":"接著把"},{"e":"pre","s":[{"e":"code","t":"&lt;IfModule dir_module&gt;\n DirectoryIndex index.html\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;"}]},{"e":"p","t":"改成"},{"e":"pre","s":[{"e":"code","t":"&lt;IfModule dir_module&gt;\n DirectoryIndex index.php index.html\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\n&lt;FilesMatch \\.php$&gt;\n SetHandler application/x-httpd-php\n&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;"}]},{"e":"p","s":[{"e":"span","t":"然後重該 Apache "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl -k restop"}]},{"e":"h3","t":"版本切換工具"},{"e":"p","t":"因版本切換時，因為都要先 unlink 再 line 太麻煩，而且還有分 CLI 與 Apache 的更改兩步驟，所以可以使用 sphp 來快速解決這問題。"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"安裝 "},{"e":"code","t":"curl -L https://gist.github.com/w00fz/142b6b19750ea6979137b963df959d11/raw &gt; /usr/local/bin/sphp"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"更改權限 "},{"e":"code","t":"chmod +x /usr/local/bin/sphp"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"安裝好後 "},{"e":"code","t":"echo $PATH"},{"e":"span","t":" 看一下有無 "},{"e":"b","t":"sphp"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"舉例，終端機直個打 sphp 就可以列出可用的 php 版本，而切換 70 版本則 "},{"e":"code","t":"sphp 70"}]}]},{"e":"h3","t":"筆記"},{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"新的 Apache conf 位置 "},{"e":"code","t":"/usr/local/etc/httpd/httpd.conf"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"新的 Apache vhosts 位置 "},{"e":"code","t":"/usr/local/etc/httpd/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"Apache 開啟 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl start"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"Apache 關閉 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl stop"}]},{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"span","t":"Apache 重開 "},{"e":"code","t":"sudo apachectl -k restart"}]}]}],"r":[{"e":"ul","s":[{"e":"li","s":[{"e":"a","attr":{"href":"https://getgrav.org/blog/macos-sierra-apache-multiple-php-versions","target":"_blank"},"t":"macOS 10.13 High Sierra Apache Setup: Multiple PHP Versions | Grav"}]}]}],"g":["macOS","Apache","PHP"]}